race.description: George Carroll Kitchens & Joinery Maiden Plate
race.comment: BROKEN IMAGE (1) resumes for the Burnett yard and reunites with the in-form Boudvillain, who has placed twice from three rides on her. Given a soft trial to tune up and looks capable of making a bold return. RITA RED (5) was good fresh here when flashing home into fourth at big odds, then backed it up with a sound placing at Corowa 16 days ago. Peaking now and shapes as the main danger. TASSY FOX (9) resumes for the local stable and picks up a key booking in McDougall, who knows her well. The maiden win has proven elusive, but she's been honest throughout and should be charging late. JENNI DIVINE (2) returns from a 320-day break without a public trial, so may need the outing, but her best form is more than good enough for this. Must be included on talent alone.
